                  <msItem>
                     <p>Daventry, The Mills.

   <persName>
                           <forename>Geoffrey</forename> son of <persName>
                              <forename>Roger</forename> the <surname>miller</surname> of <placeName role="person" key="place_108012">D<supplied>aventry</supplied>
                              </placeName>
                           </persName>
                        </persName> grants to <orgName key="org_108004">D<supplied>aventry</supplied>
                        </orgName> the croft lying between the <placeName type="minor">Almoner’s croft</placeName> and the <placeName type="street" key="place_108145">Welton road</placeName>, for which they gave him 3 marks. Witnesses: 
   <persName>Sir <forename>Robert</forename> 
                           <surname type="patronymic">fitz-Walter</surname>, kt.</persName>, 
   <persName>Sir <forename>Philip</forename> of <surname>D<supplied>aventry</supplied>
                           </surname>, kt.</persName>, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>John</forename> 
                           <surname>Gemme</surname>
                        </persName>, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>William</forename> 
                           <surname>Plumstone</surname>
                        </persName>, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>John</forename> of  <surname>Neubot</surname>
                        </persName>, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>Henry</forename> the <surname>smith</surname>
                        </persName>, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>Jordan</forename> of <surname>Uptrop</surname>
                        </persName>. 
   <origDate notBefore="1270" notAfter="1280" precision="low">
                           <supplied>c. 1270–80.</supplied>
                        </origDate>
   
                     </p>
